public interface UMLMessage
extends UMLModelElement, UMLMessage

A representation of the model object 'UML Message'.

The following features are supported:

  • Interaction
  • Activator
  • Successors
  • Predecessors
  • Arguments
  • Communication Link
  • Receiver
  • Action
  • Sender
